Installation instructions for TCdial

Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------
Soundcard with OSS or Alsa with OSS emulation.

Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------
1) % tar -zxvf tcdial-1.0.tar.gz
2) % cd tcdial-1.0
3) % make
4) copy 'dialer' somewhere in your $PATH like /usr/local/bin;
5) % dialer

TimeCop [timecop@japan.co.jp]
